abstract: Simon Dominguez's attempt to become first person to swim from Golden Gate Bridge to Farallon Islands is thwarted by great white shark.
lead_paragraph: A great white shark thwarted a Northern California man’s quest to become the first person to swim from the Golden Gate Bridge to the Farallon Islands.

headline.main: Shark Stops Man’s Attempt at Record
headline.print_headline: Sports Briefing | Swimming; Shark Stops Man’s Attempt at Record
